wiki.text:
'Bonehead' can refer to:
* an idiot
* Bonehead, a derogatory term in the skinhead and punk subcultures, referring to
  white power skinheads
* Bonehead, a derogatory term in the United Kingdom, used by traditional
  skinheads to describe punk rock-influenced skinheads
* Bonehead, a derogatory term in South Africa for an Afrikaner
* Bonehead, a character in various Comic Strip films, such as [[The
  Bullshitters: Roll out the Gunbarrel]]
* Another term for pachycephalosaurus, or other species similar to it
* Bonehead (band), a Philadelphia, Pennsylvania band
* Bonehead, a BBC TV series starring Colin Douglas
* Paul Arthurs, former Oasis rhythm guitarist who went almost exclusively by the
  nickname Bonehead
* Bonehead Merkle (1888 – 1956), a US baseball player
* [[Bone Head]] 1997 album by Half Japanese *Bonehead, a fan of the TV
  Series Bones
